47:33.934 --> 47:35.534
We were just never there for each other.

47:37.229 --> 47:38.229
And now...

47:43.361 --> 47:45.148
Why are we talking about this shit, man?

47:45.988 --> 47:47.570
I mean, we're on vacation here, right?

47:47.656 --> 47:49.272
We're supposed to be enjoying ourselves.

47:49.492 --> 47:51.609
Let's just try and enjoy tonight, okay?

47:52.870 --> 47:53.870
Cheers, brother.

47:57.333 --> 47:58.915
Perfect. There's <i>Sparkles.</i>

47:59.251 --> 48:01.091
I'm gonna go have a dance with her,
watch this.

48:02.171 --> 48:03.171
Jimmy.

48:03.756 --> 48:04.756
Jimmy.

48:05.383 --> 48:06.669
- Hey!
- You can't be up here.

48:06.759 --> 48:08.679
Seriously, you can't be up here.
Mike, it's fine.

48:08.719 --> 48:10.599
- Whoa, whoa!
- It's okay. It's fine, it's fine.

48:10.638 --> 48:12.220
