- Off the stage.

48:12.306 --> 48:14.117
- It's fine.
- Whoa, whoa. Hang on, I know her.

48:14.141 --> 48:15.723
- Jimmy.
- What are these guys...

48:16.060 --> 48:17.180
You can't come up here, man.

48:17.686 --> 48:18.686
It's Lyle Lovett.

48:19.772 --> 48:22.059
