49:51.739 --> 49:52.739
Come on, we're leaving.

49:54.617 --> 49:55.617
Let's go.

49:55.910 --> 49:56.910
Give me your keys.

49:56.994 --> 49:57.994
Milly!

49:58.746 --> 50:00.106
I hope you know what you're doing.

50:01.123 --> 50:02.123
Yeah, me, too.

50:37.701 --> 50:38.701
I found it.

50:39.078 --> 50:40.078
Found it where?

50:40.412 --> 50:42.028
This place I've been going for scrap.

50:42.289 --> 50:44.076
You found this thing in a vacant?

50:44.583 --> 50:46.728
- Let me see.
- You're drunk and you have a concussion,

50:46.752 --> 50:48.744
- I really don't...
- I'm fine. I'm fine.

50:49.630 --> 50:50.950
I just want to see it, all right?

50:51.423 --> 50:53.506
Man, somebody's got to be
looking for this thing.

50:54.134 --> 50:55.134
Oh, shit.

50:56.929 --> 50:57.929
What happened?

50:58.430 --> 50:59.295
It just closed up.

50:59.390 --> 51:00.430
Maybe it doesn't like you.

51:00.641 --> 51:02.507
- You try it.
- I'm not touching that thing.

51:08.691 --> 51:09.691
Make it work.

51:16.532 --> 51:17.693
