what it can do until back there.

51:20.202 --> 51:22.122
Yeah, but you had a pretty good idea,
didn't you?

51:23.455 --> 51:24.455
Well, shit, man.

51:24.790 --> 51:25.790
Let's see it again.

51:26.333 --> 51:27.733
Light up that haystack right there.

51:29.128 --> 51:31.745
Come on, man, don't be shy now.
You got this.

51:38.721 --> 51:39.757
