51:51.775 --> 51:53.562
This shit is crazy.

51:57.072 --> 51:59.985
- Whoa!
- Oh, my God. Oh, my God.

52:00.075 --> 52:01.441
Oh, my God.

52:01.827 --> 52:03.159
That thing is a cannon.

52:03.662 --> 52:04.698
It's insane.

52:05.080 --> 52:07.663
I can't believe we just left this thing
