52:08.083 --> 52:09.949
What, you want me
walking around with this?

52:10.044 --> 52:11.080
I can't believe this guy.

52:13.297 --> 52:14.297
Wow.

52:14.381 --> 52:16.168
Those guys' faces back at the club.

52:20.095 --> 52:21.095
Shit.

52:21.555 --> 52:23.046
- What?
- Jimmy, what?

52:23.140 --> 52:25.507
- Shit. Shit!
- What?

52:26.644 --> 52:27.644
My bag.

52:28.646 --> 52:30.558
