I left it in the bar.

52:31.899 --> 52:33.099
Well, how much are we talking?

52:33.692 --> 52:35.979
- Sixty, seventy.
- What, thousand?

52:36.070 --> 52:37.606
- Yeah.
- Thousand?

52:37.988 --> 52:39.650
