53:51.228 --> 53:52.228
Sorry.

53:54.022 --> 53:55.022
It does that.

53:55.649 --> 53:56.649
Okay.

54:00.571 --> 54:01.571
Here.

54:03.449 --> 54:04.449
Thanks.

54:09.413 --> 54:10.773
Where'd you get that on your hand?

54:12.458 --> 54:13.458
My parents.

54:13.917 --> 54:15.283
Well, my original ones.

54:16.587 --> 54:17.587
Mom or Dad?

54:18.881 --> 54:19.881
I don't know.

54:20.466 --> 54:21.832
I mean, I was just a baby, so...

54:22.176 --> 54:23.576
That's how you wound up with the...

54:25.012 --> 54:26.012
From a shelter.

54:27.639 --> 54:29.471
I mean, I was just
a couple months old, so...

54:34.438 --> 54:35.438
Check it out.

54:36.315 --> 54:38.602
