54:41.153 --> 54:43.987
Yeah. Sometimes people who aren't ready
to have kids have them anyway.

54:48.702 --> 54:49.702
What'd you do?

54:51.371 --> 54:52.371
At the time?

54:53.874 --> 54:55.536
