54:58.420 --> 54:59.956
Yeah, I left home eventually.

55:01.924 --> 55:04.404
When I was, I don't know,
a couple years older than you, maybe?

55:06.553 --> 55:08.010
Been on the move ever since.

55:11.475 --> 55:13.216
You know, I've had to say "peace"

55:13.310 --> 55:15.927
