55:18.023 --> 55:19.264
It's pretty messed up, huh?

55:19.483 --> 55:20.483
Yeah.

55:24.988 --> 55:25.988
Hey.

55:27.241 --> 55:28.241
Don't hide it, okay?

55:29.701 --> 55:30.942
It's proof you're a survivor.

55:33.831 --> 55:34.831
