and bail in the middle of the night,

57:15.474 --> 57:17.466
but, oh, wait, you're broke.

57:19.227 --> 57:20.843
- You're an asshole.
- You're an asshole.

57:30.030 --> 57:31.566
I was stuck there, all right?

57:34.076 --> 57:37.160
Lee has a way
of getting girls he likes to stay,

57:38.413 --> 57:39.745
as long as he sees fit.

57:41.208 --> 57:42.208
You feel me?

57:44.544 --> 57:46.825
The two of you guys walking in there,
handing it to him...

57:48.298 --> 57:49.298
First I'd ever seen that.

57:52.052 --> 57:54.972
I got in your truck because you guys
seemed like some good guys, you know.

57:56.014 --> 57:58.631
Plus, if you... did try anything funny,

57:58.725 --> 58:01.045
I'm pretty sure even I could take you
in a fistfight, so...

58:07.150 --> 58:08.150
To fistfights.

58:19.538 --> 58:20.538
That...

58:22.249 --> 58:23.249
